          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A 9Be beam with an intensity of approximately 3.5",
                "particle-nA was supplied by the sector-focusing",
                "cyclotron."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A stack of 20 uranium targets, each of the target is",
                "composite of one uranium target and one self-support",
                "aluminum foil with about 0.3 mg/cm2 thickness. The",
                "uranium targets were prepared by molecular plating",
                "technique, uranyl nitrate onto the 0.8 mg/cm2",
                "aluminum foil to a thickness of about 100 ug/cm2."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The scattered beam particles were detected using",
                "four Si(Au) monitors positioned symmetrically with",
                "respect to the beam axis. After the irradiation, when",
                "events from short-lived fission products were",
                "substantially reduced, the alpha radioactivity of the",
                "long-lived 242Cm on Al catcher foils was measured by",
                "using silicon detectors placed in an off-line chamber."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " After a delaying period of more than 80 d, in",
                "order to allow the short-living activity originating",
                "from the fission products to decay out, the alpha",
                "radioactivity of 242Cm on the catcher was measured in",
                "an off-line chamber."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The cross section error included the",
                "number of alpha particles detected, the thickness of",
                "the uranium target, the geometry efficiency of the",
                "detector and the beam intensity in average."
              ]
            }
          ],
